name: GeekQuoteoftheDay
0:
”Alexa, open Geek Quote.”
”Alexa, ask Geek Quote to give me a new quote.”
”Alexa, ask Geek Quote what's the quote of the day.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: geek quote
des: With Geek Quote of the Day, you can ask Alexa for a wide variety of interesting and amusing quotes from movies, books, video games, and more! Don't like the quote you heard, or you've heard a quote before? Just ask Geek Quote for a new one. More quotes are being added to the skill all the time!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
